N1.name: Anxiety
N1.High: You often feel tense, jittery, and fearful. You may worry about things that might go wrong.
N1.Average: You generally feel calm, but can experience anxiety in stressful situations.
N1.Low: You are calm, fearless, and not easily rattled. You rarely worry about the future.

N2.name: Anger
N2.High: You have a tendency to feel angry or bitter. You may be quick to take offense.
N2.Average: You get angry occasionally when provoked, but it passes relatively quickly.
N2.Low: You are slow to anger and rarely hold grudges. You are generally easygoing.

N3.name: Depression
N3.High: You tend to feel sad, dejected, and discouraged. You may lack energy and motivation.
N3.Average: You have ups and downs in mood, but generally feel content.
N3.Low: You are generally cheerful, optimistic, and free from depressive feelings.

N4.name: Self-Consciousness
N4.High: You are sensitive about what others think of you. You may feel awkward in social situations.
N4.Average: You are reasonably comfortable in social situations, though you may feel shy occasionally.
N4.Low: You are confident and not easily embarrassed. You don't worry much about social judgment.

N5.name: Immoderation
N5.High: You may have difficulty resisting temptations and cravings. You might overindulge at times.
N5.Average: You can resist temptations most of the time, but may give in occasionally.
N5.Low: You have high self-control and can easily resist temptations and cravings.

N6.name: Vulnerability
N6.High: You feel overwhelmed by stress and pressure. You may panic in emergency situations.
N6.Average: You handle stress reasonably well, though major crises can be difficult.
N6.Low: You are resilient and handle stress and pressure with grace. You are 'cool under fire'.

E1.name: Friendliness
E1.High: You are genuinely interested in others and make friends easily. You are warm and affectionate.
E1.Average: You are friendly but not overly demonstrative. You have a few close friends.
E1.Low: You are reserved and distant. You may not seek out close relationships.

E2.name: Gregariousness
E2.High: You love the company of others and find social gatherings stimulating.
E2.Average: You enjoy social occasions but also value your privacy and alone time.
E2.Low: You prefer to be alone or with a few close friends. You find crowds draining.

E3.name: Assertiveness
E3.High: You are dominant, forceful, and comfortable taking charge. You are a natural leader.
E3.Average: You can take charge when necessary, but don't constantly seek leadership roles.
E3.Low: You prefer to stay in the background and let others lead. You are quiet and unassuming.

E4.name: Activity Level
E4.High: You lead a fast-paced, busy life. You are energetic and always on the go.
E4.Average: You have a moderate energy level. You can be busy but also enjoy relaxing.
E4.Low: You prefer a slower, more leisurely pace. You are not hurried or energetic.

E5.name: Excitement-Seeking
E5.High: You crave excitement, adventure, and stimulation. You may take risks for the thrill.
E5.Average: You enjoy some excitement but also appreciate safety and stability.
E5.Low: You prefer a safe, predictable life. You avoid risks and loud, thrilling activities.

E6.name: Cheerfulness
E6.High: You are typically full of joy, happiness, and positive energy.
E6.Average: You are generally in a good mood, but not constantly exuberant.
E6.Low: You are not typically exuberant or high-spirited. You may be serious or reserved.

O1.name: Imagination
O1.High: You have a vivid imagination and enjoy fantasy. You are creative and original.
O1.Average: You have a normal imagination but prefer the real world to fantasy.
O1.Low: You are practical and down-to-earth. You prefer facts to fantasy.

O2.name: Artistic Interests
O2.High: You love beauty in art and nature. You are easily moved by poetry, music, or art.
O2.Average: You appreciate art and beauty but are not deeply absorbed by it.
O2.Low: You are not particularly interested in art or aesthetic experiences.

O3.name: Emotionality
O3.High: You are aware of your own feelings and experience emotions intensely.
O3.Average: You experience a normal range of emotions but are not overwhelmed by them.
O3.Low: You do not pay much attention to your feelings. Your emotions are somewhat blunted.

O4.name: Adventurousness
O4.High: You are eager to try new activities, travel to new places, and experience different things.
O4.Average: You enjoy some variety but also like your familiar routines.
O4.Low: You prefer the familiar and predictable. You are uncomfortable with change.

O5.name: Intellect
O5.High: You love to play with ideas. You are open-minded and enjoy intellectual challenges.
O5.Average: You are intellectually curious but not constantly seeking complex puzzles.
O5.Low: You prefer dealing with people or things rather than abstract ideas.

O6.name: Liberalism
O6.High: You are ready to challenge authority and convention. You value freedom and diversity.
O6.Average: You hold a mix of traditional and progressive views.
O6.Low: You are conservative and value tradition. You prefer established ways of doing things.

A1.name: Trust
A1.High: You believe that most people are honest and well-intentioned.
A1.Average: You are generally trusting but not naive. You are cautious when necessary.
A1.Low: You are cynical and skeptical. You assume people may be dishonest or dangerous.

A2.name: Morality
A2.High: You are frank, sincere, and candid. You would never use deception.
A2.Average: You are generally honest, but may be guarded or diplomatic when needed.
A2.Low: You are willing to use deception or manipulation if it serves your purpose.

A3.name: Altruism
A3.High: You find helping others genuinely rewarding. You are generous and considerate.
A3.Average: You are willing to help others, but not at the expense of your own needs.
A3.Low: You are somewhat self-centered and reluctant to get involved in others' problems.

A4.name: Cooperation
A4.High: You dislike confrontation. You are willing to compromise to get along with others.
A4.Average: You can compromise, but will stand up for your needs if pushed.
A4.Low: You are aggressive and competitive. You prefer to win rather than compromise.

A5.name: Modesty
A5.High: You are humble and self-effacing. You do not like to brag.
A5.Average: You have a healthy self-esteem but are not arrogant.
A5.Low: You think highly of yourself and may be seen as arrogant or conceited.

A6.name: Sympathy
A6.High: You are tender-hearted and compassionate. You feel others' pain.
A6.Average: You are sympathetic but try to remain objective.
A6.Low: You are hard-headed and tough-minded. You are not easily moved by pity.

C1.name: Self-Efficacy
C1.High: You feel prepared to deal with life. You are confident in your ability to succeed.
C1.Average: You feel reasonably capable, though you may doubt yourself at times.
C1.Low: You feel ineffective and unprepared. You may lack confidence in your abilities.

C2.name: Orderliness
C2.High: You are extremely well-organized, neat, and tidy. You live by schedules.
C2.Average: You are generally organized but can be messy at times.
C2.Low: You are unorganized and unmethodical. You may leave things in a mess.

C3.name: Dutifulness
C3.High: You have a strong sense of moral obligation. You always keep your promises.
C3.Average: You are dependable and reliable, but not rigidly so.
C3.Low: You find rules and regulations confining. You may be unreliable at times.

C4.name: Achievement-Striving
C4.High: You strive hard to achieve excellence. You have high aspirations.
C4.Average: You work hard but are not a workaholic. You have a balanced approach.
C4.Low: You are content with getting by. You are not driven by ambition.

C5.name: Self-Discipline
C5.High: You have the willpower to persist at difficult or unpleasant tasks.
C5.Average: You can get work done, but may procrastinate on difficult tasks.
C5.Low: You tend to procrastinate and have poor follow-through. You are easily distracted.

C6.name: Cautiousness
C6.High: You are deliberate and think carefully before acting. You avoid mistakes.
C6.Average: You usually think before acting, but can be spontaneous.
C6.Low: You are hasty and impulsive. You often act without thinking of the consequences.
